snippet.title: Aquaman (2018) Interview with Jason Momoa, Amber Heard & Cast
snippet.description:
Studio Movie Grill correspondent, Danielle Hawthorne (insta: @danielle.hawthorne) headed all the way down to Atlantis to chat with the cast of Aquaman. 

Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and be a hero to the world. 

With: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Patrick Wilson, James Wan and Danielle Hawthorne 

Get tickets to see Aquaman at Studio Movie Grill: http://bit.ly/2Q8IJqz 

Genre: Action, Adventure & Fantasy
